<p>Hi <%= @resource.account %>,</p>
<p>We received a request to reset your password for your CDS account: <%= @resource.email %>. We're here to help!</p>
<p>Simply click on the link to set a new password: <%= link_to  'Change password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token)  %></p>
<p>If you didn't ask to change your password, don't worry! Your password is still safe and you can ignore this email.</p>
<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>The CDS System</p>
